OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy on Wednesday, with rain likely
OL,7,Fby the evening. A frosty start on
OL,8,FThursday but then fine and sunny.
OL,9,FOvernight rain clearing to sunny
OL,10,Fspells on Friday. Turning colder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
